{"id": "1506693575738396832", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "content": "\"Team Unique\" is antiquated and I was told at one point that they intend to remove it entirely.\n\nIt's not possible to equip the same Wheel to two different Awakeners, so it's implied that the effects are Team Unique.\n\nFor effects that multiple Wheels have that don't stack with each other, I put \"*(Does not stack with other Wheels.)*\" See Wheel Unseen, Uteri Somnia etc.", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T16:22:21.469000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["265494179222650891"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "celeste_ok", "emoji_id": "1408324285147254855", "count": 1}], "reply_to": "1506692913030234313"}
